# Portfolio Design Guidelines

## Visual Style

- Minimal, modern, clean
- Dark/light mode support
- Consistent typography hierarchy

## Hero Section

- Strong headline + short intro
- Call-to-action (View Projects, Contact)
- Subtle background (grid, gradient, animation)

## Projects Section

- Show real projects only
- Include:
  - Title
  - Description
  - Tech stack
  - Live/demo link

## Skills

- Categorize (Frontend, Backend, Tools)
- Avoid long unstructured lists

## UX

- Fast loading
- Smooth scroll
- Clear navigation

## Content

- Focus on impact, not just tools
- Avoid generic descriptions